# Frontend Configuration

## Environment Variables

Create `.env.local` file:

```env
# Supabase
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=your_supabase_url
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_supabase_anon_key

# Backend API
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:5001
NEXT_PUBLIC_SOCKET_URL=http://localhost:5001

# Collaborative Editing (Yjs WebSocket)
NEXT_PUBLIC_COLLAB_WS_URL=ws://localhost:1234

# App Config
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_NAME=Mentor Sessions
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000
```

## Features

- Authentication with Supabase
- Real-time collaborative code editor with Yjs (CRDT)
- Video conferencing with WebRTC
- Chat system with Socket.io
- Responsive design with Tailwind CSS
- Purple, Green, Yellow glowing theme

## Development

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

Visit `http://localhost:3000`
